  <brief_title>Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of CTP-543 in Adult Patients With Moderate to Severe Alopecia Areata</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-Blind, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of CTP-543 in Adult Patients With Moderate to Severe Alopecia Areata</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
